        public static final Image.Format RGB16F_to_RGB111110F

      • RGB111110F

        public static final Image.Format RGB111110F

      • RGB16F_to_RGB9E5

        public static final Image.Format RGB16F_to_RGB9E5
        Texture data is stored as RGB16F in system memory, but will be converted to RGB9E5 when sent to the video hardware. Requires Caps.FloatTexture and Caps.SharedExponentTexture.

        public static final Image.Format RGB9E5
